    "The AAEC results are displayed in Table 4.",
    "The findings imply that considerable performance improvements are typically obtained by increasing the parameters.",
    "Our models' performance is significantly improved when utilising models with billion-scale parameters, even though they do not outperform stateof-the-art models when using base or large models.",
